('7', 'service-7', 'Content Marketing', 'Creating valuable and engaging content', '<p>Attract and retain your target audience with our content marketing services. We develop content strategies and create high-quality content that resonates with your users and drives engagement.</p><p>Our services include blog posts, articles, whitepapers, case studies, and social media content.</p>', 'Engaging content for your audience.', 'https://picsum.photos/id/1075/800/600', 'Content Marketing Image', 'Content Marketing | Zirospace', 'Create compelling content with Zirospace.', '["content marketing", "blogging", "copywriting", "whitepapers", "case studies"]', true, 6, NOW(), NOW()),
